{"tid":2401877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曼谷自來水變鹹","createTime":"2021-02-10T05:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T05:46:03.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"82e5c1fc783d6192d09ac8f6c2f996bbcbe28637","tid":2401877,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"泰叻報報導，針對曼谷自來水變鹹一事，大都會水務局（Metropolitan Waterworks Authority）表示，受季節性因素影響，整個2月的海水水位都高於昭披耶河的水位，導致部分地區的自來水出現鹹味，尤其到15日前會特別明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「這次自來水變鹹持續的時間將比之前還要久。」大都會水務局副局長兼發言人孔克里（Komkrit Dinakara Na Ayudhya）說，「身體健康情況良好民眾可如常飲用，但最好調整食物攝取方式；慢性病病患則要避免。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孔克里指出，有腎臟或心臟疾病民眾，或高血壓、糖尿病患者，以及長者、嬰幼兒及小型寵物，應避免直接飲用自來水。且他還說，即便是將自來水煮沸鹹味也不會消失，因為煮沸只會將水蒸發，反而使得鹽分更濃縮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孔克里另表示，大都會水務局已協調皇家灌溉廳、曼谷污水處理廳等單位，合作處理自來水偏鹹的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，大都會水務局也建議民眾上該局官網追蹤自來水水質，或透過水務局官方臉書、推特、Line、Instagram帳號，「@MWAthailand」進行查看，也能下載水利局的App。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或民眾可以自備空瓶、容器，到離家最近的水務局各地辦公室裝飲用水。等海水水位下降，自來水品質恢復正常時，水務局也會提醒民眾何時可儲水備用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼谷椰子新聞網報導，水資源官員頌奇（Somkiat Prajamwong）則認為，曼谷地區自來水出現鹹味的情形可能要到雨季來臨時才會改善。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n頌奇說，最近一直到3月是暴風天氣的好發期，這會對昭披耶河及三角洲地區內水位造成影響，加上前一段時間的旱象，種種原因使得河水更鹹。情況在4月後會逐漸改善，5月雨季來臨時將恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為了緩解鹽化狀況，頌奇表示，昭披耶河、美功河流域6座水壩會放水共5億立方公尺，協助降低因海水水位上升灌入淡水後升高的鹽分。他說水源處理設備對自來水質的改善，可望在2023年有明顯成效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTXFvJa.jpg&amp;h=eee4f1dd&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"ace4a2ff20a1830333691631b4b4dfb75e085c36","tid":2401877,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxRnGYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxRnGYD.jpg&h=81fb6096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzuoVzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzuoVzs.jpg&h=019d6bbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4dc67f951c42d71e9053d5510be58360f09dcf5","tid":2401877,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"呢位泰中人係邊位"},{"pid":"f9d5f76e71fc80c5d1e97120a091abfe57fd9b4e","tid":2401877,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4dc67f951c42d71e9053d5510be58360f09dcf5","tid":2401877,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:22:13.000Z","msg":"呢位泰中人係邊位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3X8YXO6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3X8YXO6.png&h=5581ca7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4e7a2a780ad9b6d193f0dba96207f30726f33a0","tid":2401877,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ace4a2ff20a1830333691631b4b4dfb75e085c36","tid":2401877,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxRnGYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxRnGYD.jpg&h=81fb6096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DzuoVzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDzuoVzs.jpg&h=019d6bbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09670ba9e21c68045191ef309da9712cc6ce5fe","tid":2401877,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"越飲咪越渴囉"},{"pid":"40678973559c51ae6a9663a01094542e0155e62e","tid":2401877,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b09670ba9e21c68045191ef309da9712cc6ce5fe","tid":2401877,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"越飲咪越渴囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"你估真係變海水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7fc320f95602bfc2b4422514c1d9f025b7bf14","tid":2401877